+//   lands later via 14-MS T-030.
+// NUMERIC-exact: qty_held_kg / affected_qty_kg / yield / claim columns are NUMERIC (never float).
+//
+// Soft cross-module references (reason_code_id, reference_id, product_id, fail_reason_code_id,
